CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 2, 1966, pg. 12A, reads: "Bags Two - Ed Parson of Uniontown High School drives in for a two pointer as Schenley's Ed Gibson zooms past him in vain effort to get the ball... Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Uniontown High School basketball player Ed Parson dunking basketball in game against Schenley, University of Pittsburgh Field House
